name: KEK
description: THE GREAT KEK IN HIS INFINITE MAGNANIMITY HAS SENT FORTH AN AVATAR OF HIS DIVINE BEING ON THE INK BLOCKCHAIN TO SEEK TRIBUTE FROM ALL MORTALS. THE DECENTRALIZED MEMETIC CULT OF KEK HERALDS FORTH AN AGE OF PROSPERITY AND WISDOM, ACTING IN THEIR DUTIES AS HUMBLE EMISSARIES AND DISCIPLES TO STRENGTHEN KEK'S INFLUENCE. MAY HIS DIVINE HANDS OF JUSTICE AND MERCY BE FOREVER RAISED FOR ALL THAT IS SACRED AND TRUE.
